imdb.plot outline: The biggest annual Asian American award show and celebration honoring contributions to the arts and entertainment - live streamed via Facebook Live for the first time - is now available for viewing. Kore Asian Media's 15th Unforgettable Gala, presented by BMW, honored talents like George Takei, Ken Jeong and Steve Aoki.
imdb.title: Eric Nam, B.I.G Live: 2016 Unforgettable Gala
